            "highlighted_scribble": "circle"
          }
        },
        "testimonial_cMqe8h": {
          "type": "testimonial",
          "settings": {
            "icon": "quote",
            "text": "<p>Holy grail of wedges! They are the most comfortable wedges ever! I wear them all day with no issues. The arch support is fantastic.</p>",
            "author": "Sherri J.",
            "author_info": "",
            "author_url": "",
            "image_ratio": "rounded",
            "highlighted_text": "none",
            "highlighted_scribble": "circle"
          }
        },
        "testimonial_DUKJrG": {
          "type": "testimonial",
          "settings": {
            "icon": "quote",
            "text": "<p>Highly recommend! Love these shoes! The Ashley Arch Support Wedge is not only fashionable but also comfortable to wear from the get-go.</p>",
            "author": "Julie S.",
            "author_info": "",
            "author_url": "",
            "image_ratio": "rounded",
            "highlighted_text": "none",
            "highlighted_scribble": "circle"
          }
        },
        "testimonial_KMjBFE": {
          "type": "testimonial",
          "settings": {
            "icon": "quote",
            "text": "<p>These are wonderful shoes. I have high arches and very bad knee arthritis. I never wear heels, but these are a real exception. I can wear them all day without exacerbating my knee pain, and they look great!</p>",
            "author": "Joan S.",
            "author_info": "",
            "author_url": "",
            "image_ratio": "rounded",
            "highlighted_text": "none",
            "highlighted_scribble": "circle"
          }
        },
        "testimonial_J6K3XV": {
          "type": "testimonial",
          "settings": {
            "icon": "quote",
            "text": "<p>What a great shoe! This is the most comfortable shoe I own. The arch support is perfect and the adjustable straps are terrific. All of this and stylish too!</p>",
            "author": "Kathy C.",
            "author_info": "",
            "author_url": "",
            "image_ratio": "rounded",
            "highlighted_text": "none",
            "highlighted_scribble": "circle"
          }
        },
        "testimonial_AQFrnV": {
          "type": "testimonial",
          "settings": {
            "icon": "quote",
            "text": "<p>These shoes are great! They give me arch support and a soft footbed, as well as adjustable straps. And they are pretty!!</p>",
            "author": "Kristin L.",
            "author_info": "",
            "author_url": "",
            "image_ratio": "rounded",
